{
  "video_id": "ULNPLFrTirQ",
  "title": "Lifesaving scientific tools made of paper | Manu Prakash",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12970.0,
      "end_time": 16105.0,
      "text": "So, I love making tools and sharing them with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16938.0,
      "end_time": 18328.0,
      "text": "I remember as a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18352.0,
      "end_time": 21645.0,
      "text": "my first tool I built was actually a microscope"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21669.0,
      "end_time": 25341.0,
      "text": "that I built by stealing lenses from my brother&#39;s eyeglasses."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26109.0,
      "end_time": 27896.0,
      "text": "He wasn&#39;t that thrilled."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27920.0,
      "end_time": 30900.0,
      "text": "But, you know, maybe because of that moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30114.0,
      "end_time": 31267.0,
      "text": "30 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31291.0,
      "end_time": 33179.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m still making microscopes."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34179.0,
      "end_time": 37478.0,
      "text": "And the reason I built these tools is for moments like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39379.0,
      "end_time": 41799.0,
      "text": "(Video) Girl: I have black things in my hair --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41823.0,
      "end_time": 44980.0,
      "text": "Manu Prakash: This is a school in the Bay Area."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44660.0,
      "end_time": 49123.0,
      "text": "(Video) MP: The living world far supersedes our imagination"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49148.0,
      "end_time": 51115.0,
      "text": "of how things actually work."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51139.0,
      "end_time": 53590.0,
      "text": "(Video) Boy: Oh my God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55593.0,
      "end_time": 57945.0,
      "text": "MP: Right -- oh my God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58441.0,
      "end_time": 61442.0,
      "text": "I hadn&#39;t realized this would be such a universal phrase."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62943.0,
      "end_time": 64742.0,
      "text": "Over the last two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64766.00000000001,
      "end_time": 65934.0,
      "text": "in my lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65958.0,
      "end_time": 68330.0,
      "text": "we built 50,000 Foldscopes"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68570.0,
      "end_time": 70967.0,
      "text": "and shipped them to 130 countries in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70991.0,
      "end_time": 73577.0,
      "text": "at no cost to the kids we sent them to."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74580.0,
      "end_time": 75301.0,
      "text": "This year alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75325.0,
      "end_time": 77457.0,
      "text": "with the support of our community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77481.0,
      "end_time": 79961.0,
      "text": "we are planning to ship a million microscopes"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79985.0,
      "end_time": 81347.0,
      "text": "to kids around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81854.0,
      "end_time": 83423.0,
      "text": "What does that do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83448.0,
      "end_time": 87204.0,
      "text": "It creates an inspiring community of people around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87228.0,
      "end_time": 88899.0,
      "text": "learning and teaching each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88924.0,
      "end_time": 93140.0,
      "text": "from Kenya to Kampala to Kathmandu to Kansas."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93380.0,
      "end_time": 95683.0,
      "text": "And one of the phenomenal things that I love about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95707.0,
      "end_time": 97262.0,
      "text": "is the sense of community."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 97691.0,
      "end_time": 99830.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a kid in Nicaragua"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99107.0,
      "end_time": 103301.0,
      "text": "teaching others how to identify mosquito species that carry dengue"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 103325.0,
      "end_time": 105743.0,
      "text": "by looking at the larva under a microscope."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105767.0,
      "end_time": 108315.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a pharmacologist who came up with a new way"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108339.0,
      "end_time": 110582.0,
      "text": "to detect fake drugs anywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111222.0,
      "end_time": 113280.0,
      "text": "There is a girl who wondered:"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113305.0,
      "end_time": 115300.0,
      "text": "\"How does glitter actually work?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115270.0,
      "end_time": 118746.0,
      "text": "and discovered the physics of crystalline formation in glitter."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119533.0,
      "end_time": 121138.0,
      "text": "There is an Argentinian doctor"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121162.0,
      "end_time": 125424.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s trying to do field cervical cancer screening with this tool."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125448.0,
      "end_time": 129186.0,
      "text": "And yours very truly found a species of flea"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129210.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133986.0,
      "text": "that was dug inside my heel in my foot one centimeter deep."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135141.0,
      "end_time": 139398.0,
      "text": "Now, you might think of these as anomalies."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139795.0,
      "end_time": 141815.0,
      "text": "But there is a method to this madness."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 142437.0,
      "end_time": 144667.0,
      "text": "I call this \"frugal science\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 144691.0,
      "end_time": 148543.0,
      "text": "the idea of sharing the experience of science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148567.0,
      "end_time": 150282.0,
      "text": "and not just the information."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150831.0,
      "end_time": 152460.0,
      "text": "To remind you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 152700.0,
      "end_time": 154154.0,
      "text": "there are a billion people on this planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154178.0,
      "end_time": 156692.0,
      "text": "who live with absolutely no infrastructure:"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156717.0,
      "end_time": 158331.0,
      "text": "no roads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 158355.0,
      "end_time": 159737.0,
      "text": "no electricity"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 159761.0,
      "end_time": 161547.0,
      "text": "and thus, no health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 162787.0,
      "end_time": 167230.0,
      "text": "Also, there a billion kids on this planet that live in poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167520.0,
      "end_time": 169188.0,
      "text": "How are we supposed to inspire them"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169212.0,
      "end_time": 171534.0,
      "text": "for the next generation of solution makers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 172840.0,
      "end_time": 174832.0,
      "text": "There are health care workers that we put on the line"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174856.0,
      "end_time": 176774.0,
      "text": "to fight infectious diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 176798.0,
      "end_time": 181255.0,
      "text": "to protect us with absolutely bare-minimum tools and resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182404.0,
      "end_time": 183998.0,
      "text": "So as a lab at Stanford,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184220.0,
      "end_time": 187959.0,
      "text": "I think of this from a context of frugal science"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 187983.0,
      "end_time": 190568.0,
      "text": "and building solutions for these communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 190592.0,
      "end_time": 195174.0,
      "text": "Often we think about being able to do diagnosis under a tree, off-grid."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 195636.0,
      "end_time": 198365.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll tell you two examples today of new tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 198389.0,
      "end_time": 200194.0,
      "text": "One of them starts in Uganda."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 200571.0,
      "end_time": 202100.0,
      "text": "In 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 202124.0,
      "end_time": 206170.0,
      "text": "on a field trip to detect schistosomiasis with Foldscopes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 206194.0,
      "end_time": 208751.0,
      "text": "I made a minor observation."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 208776.0,
      "end_time": 210353.0,
      "text": "In a clinic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210377.0,
      "end_time": 211716.0,
      "text": "in a far, remote area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 211740.0,
      "end_time": 215328.0,
      "text": "I saw a centrifuge being used as a doorstop."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 216120.0,
      "end_time": 218403.0,
      "text": "I mean -- quite literally, the doorstop."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 218427.0,
      "end_time": 220153.0,
      "text": "And I asked them and they said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 220177.0,
      "end_time": 222203.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, we don&#39;t actually have electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 222228.0,
      "end_time": 225757.0,
      "text": "so this piece of junk is good as a doorstop.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 226444.0,
      "end_time": 229146.0,
      "text": "Centrifuges, for some of you who don&#39;t know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 229170.0,
      "end_time": 232393.0,
      "text": "are the pinnacle tool to be able to do sample processing."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 232418.0,
      "end_time": 235160.0,
      "text": "You separate components of blood or body fluids"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 235184.0,
      "end_time": 237644.0,
      "text": "to be able to detect and identify pathogens."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 238239.0,
      "end_time": 241730.0,
      "text": "But centrifuges are bulky, expensive --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241970.0,
      "end_time": 243291.0,
      "text": "cost around 1,000 dollars --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243315.0,
      "end_time": 245321.0,
      "text": "and really hard to carry out in the field."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 245345.0,
      "end_time": 246502.0,
      "text": "And of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 246526.0,
      "end_time": 247960.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t work without power."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 247984.0,
      "end_time": 249376.0,
      "text": "Sound familiar?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 249400.0,
      "end_time": 251948.0,
      "text": "So we started thinking about solving this problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 251972.0,
      "end_time": 253522.0,
      "text": "and I came back --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 253546.0,
      "end_time": 255212.0,
      "text": "kept thinking about toys."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 255638.0,
      "end_time": 256802.0,
      "text": "Now ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 257850.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259608.00000000003,
      "text": "I have a few with me here."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 259632.0,
      "end_time": 261739.0,
      "text": "I first started with yo-yos ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 261762.0,
      "end_time": 264393.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m a terrible yo-yo thrower."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 264743.0,
      "end_time": 266424.0,
      "text": "Because these objects spin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 266448.0,
      "end_time": 267609.0,
      "text": "we wondered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 267634.0,
      "end_time": 269991.0,
      "text": "could we actually use the physics of these objects"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 270150.0,
      "end_time": 271724.0,
      "text": "to be able to build centrifuges?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 273770.0,
      "end_time": 275567.0,
      "text": "This was possibly the worst throw I could make."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 276256.0,
      "end_time": 277748.0,
      "text": "But you might start realizing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 277773.0,
      "end_time": 280612.0,
      "text": "if you start exploring the space of toys --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 280636.0,
      "end_time": 283241.0,
      "text": "we tried these spinning tops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 283265.0,
      "end_time": 285147.0,
      "text": "and then in the lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 285171.0,
      "end_time": 287253.0,
      "text": "we stumbled upon this wonder."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 287590.0,
      "end_time": 291750.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the whirligig, or a buzzer, or a rundle."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 291100.0,
      "end_time": 293517.0,
      "text": "A couple of strings and a little disk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 293541.0,
      "end_time": 295748.0,
      "text": "and if I push, it spins."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 296170.0,
      "end_time": 298514.0,
      "text": "How many of you have played with this as a kid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 298538.0,
      "end_time": 300386.0,
      "text": "This is called a button-on-a-string."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 300410.0,
      "end_time": 302460.0,
      "text": "OK, maybe 50 percent of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 302700.0,
      "end_time": 303628.0,
      "text": "What you didn&#39;t realize --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 303652.0,
      "end_time": 305965.0,
      "text": "that this little object"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 305989.0,
      "end_time": 310352.0,
      "text": "is the oldest toy in the history of mankind ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 310827.0,
      "end_time": 312472.0,
      "text": "5,000 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 312496.0,
      "end_time": 316195.0,
      "text": "We have found relics of this object hidden around on our planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 316924.0,
      "end_time": 318864.0,
      "text": "Now the irony is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 318889.0,
      "end_time": 322624.0,
      "text": "we actually don&#39;t understand how this little thing works."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 322648.0,
      "end_time": 324510.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when I get excited."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 324617.0,
      "end_time": 326698.0,
      "text": "So we got back to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 326722.0,
      "end_time": 328512.0,
      "text": "wrote down a couple of equations."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 328876.0,
      "end_time": 332188.0,
      "text": "If you take the input torque that you put in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 332213.0,
      "end_time": 334317.0,
      "text": "you take the drag on this disc,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 334341.0,
      "end_time": 336246.0,
      "text": "and the twist drag on these strings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 336270.0,
      "end_time": 338758.0,
      "text": "you should be able to mathematically solve this."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 338783.0,
      "end_time": 341591.0,
      "text": "This is not the only equation in my talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 341615.0,
      "end_time": 343447.0,
      "text": "Ten pages of math later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 343471.0,
      "end_time": 346330.0,
      "text": "we could actually write down the complete analytical solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 346354.0,
      "end_time": 347628.0,
      "text": "for this dynamic system."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 348208.0,
      "end_time": 351819.0,
      "text": "And out comes what we call \"Paperfuge.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 351843.0,
      "end_time": 354387.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s my postdoc Saad Bhamla,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 354411.0,
      "end_time": 356780.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s the co-inventor of Paperfuge."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 356102.0,
      "end_time": 358347.0,
      "text": "And to the left, you see all the centrifuges"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 358371.0,
      "end_time": 359798.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re trying to replace."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 359822.0,
      "end_time": 363529.0,
      "text": "This little object that you see right here"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 364759.0,
      "end_time": 368400.0,
      "text": "is a disc, a couple of strings and a handle."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 368280.0,
      "end_time": 369202.0,
      "text": "And when I spin"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 369760.0,
      "end_time": 370913.0,
      "text": "and I push,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 370937.0,
      "end_time": 372890.0,
      "text": "it starts to spin."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 372113.0,
      "end_time": 374198.0,
      "text": "Now, when you realize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 374770.0,
      "end_time": 376164.0,
      "text": "when you do the math,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 377399.0,
      "end_time": 379889.0,
      "text": "when we calculate the rpm for this object,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 379913.0,
      "end_time": 384645.0,
      "text": "mathematically, we should be able to go all the way to a million rpm."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 384669.0,
      "end_time": 386861.0,
      "text": "Now, there is a little twist in human anatomy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 386886.0,
      "end_time": 389961.0,
      "text": "because the resonant frequency of this object is about 10 hertz,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 389985.0,
      "end_time": 391789.0,
      "text": "and if you&#39;ve ever played the piano,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 391813.0,
      "end_time": 393907.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t go higher than two or three hertz."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 393931.0,
      "end_time": 397195.0,
      "text": "The maximum speed we&#39;ve been able to achieve with this object"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 397219.0,
      "end_time": 399147.0,
      "text": "is not 10,000 rpm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 399172.0,
      "end_time": 400776.0,
      "text": "not 50,000 rpm --"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 400800.0,
      "end_time": 402725.0,
      "text": "120,000 rpm."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 402749.0,
      "end_time": 405553.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s equal to 30,000 g-forces."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 405577.0,
      "end_time": 408784.0,
      "text": "If I was to stick you right here and have it spin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 408808.0,
      "end_time": 412236.0,
      "text": "you would think about the types of forces you would experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 412261.0,
      "end_time": 414499.0,
      "text": "One of the factors of a tool like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 414523.0,
      "end_time": 417517.0,
      "text": "is to be able to do diagnosis with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 417541.0,
      "end_time": 421820.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;m going to do a quick demo here, where --"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 422262.0,
      "end_time": 425857.0,
      "text": "this is a moment where I&#39;m going to make a little finger prick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 425881.0,
      "end_time": 428155.0,
      "text": "and a tiny drop of blood is going to come out."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 428180.0,
      "end_time": 430801.0,
      "text": "If you don&#39;t like blood, you don&#39;t have to look at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 430825.0,
      "end_time": 432164.0,
      "text": "Here is a little lancet."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 432188.0,
      "end_time": 434580.0,
      "text": "These lancets are available everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 434820.0,
      "end_time": 435605.0,
      "text": "completely passive."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 435629.0,
      "end_time": 439215.0,
      "text": "And if I&#39;ve had breakfast today ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 441867.0,
      "end_time": 443354.0,
      "text": "That didn&#39;t hurt at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 443378.0,
      "end_time": 447361.0,
      "text": "OK, I take a little capillary with a drop of blood --"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 447386.0,
      "end_time": 449645.0,
      "text": "now this drop of blood has answers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 449669.0,
      "end_time": 451347.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s why I&#39;m interested in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 451730.0,
      "end_time": 455197.0,
      "text": "It might actually tell me whether I have malaria right now or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 455221.0,
      "end_time": 457530.0,
      "text": "I take a little capillary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 457770.0,
      "end_time": 459202.0,
      "text": "and you see it starts wicking in."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 459708.0,
      "end_time": 461976.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to draw a little more blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 464602.0,
      "end_time": 466844.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s good enough for right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 467339.0,
      "end_time": 471469.0,
      "text": "Now, I just seal this capillary by putting it in clay."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 475312.0,
      "end_time": 477592.0,
      "text": "And now that&#39;s sealed the sample."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 477616.0,
      "end_time": 479745.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to take the sample,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 479769.0,
      "end_time": 481733.0,
      "text": "mount it on Paperfuge."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 488912.0,
      "end_time": 492299.0,
      "text": "A little piece of tape to make a sealed cavity."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 492795.0,
      "end_time": 495690.0,
      "text": "So now the sample is completely enclosed."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 498927.0,
      "end_time": 501220.0,
      "text": "And we are ready for a spin."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 502839.0,
      "end_time": 504880.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m pushing and pulling with this object."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 504904.0,
      "end_time": 506603.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to load this up ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 508970.0,
      "end_time": 510380.0,
      "text": "And you see the object starts spinning."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 510404.0,
      "end_time": 512418.0,
      "text": "Unlike a regular centrifuge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 512442.0,
      "end_time": 516221.0,
      "text": "this is a counter-rotating centrifuge."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 516245.0,
      "end_time": 518581.0,
      "text": "It goes back and forth, back and forth ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 519409.99999999994,
      "end_time": 521168.99999999994,
      "text": "And now I&#39;m charging it up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 521193.0,
      "end_time": 523200.0,
      "text": "and you see it builds momentum."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 524500.0,
      "end_time": 526617.0,
      "text": "And now -- I don&#39;t know if you can hear this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 526641.0,
      "end_time": 528180.0,
      "text": "30 seconds of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 528809.0,
      "end_time": 533134.0,
      "text": "and I should be able to separate all the blood cells with the plasma."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 533758.0,
      "end_time": 536571.0,
      "text": "And the ratio of those blood  cells to plasma --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 536595.0,
      "end_time": 538609.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 540259.0,
      "end_time": 542594.0,
      "text": "Already, if you see right here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 544260.0,
      "end_time": 545650.0,
      "text": "if you focus on this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 545674.0,
      "end_time": 548218.0,
      "text": "you should be able to see a separated volume"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 549920.0,
      "end_time": 550949.0,
      "text": "of blood and plasma."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 550974.0,
      "end_time": 554897.0,
      "text": "And the ratio of that actually tells me whether I might be anemic."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 554921.0,
      "end_time": 558958.0,
      "text": "One of the aspects of this is, we build many types of Paperfuges."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 558982.0,
      "end_time": 563448.0,
      "text": "This one allows us to identify malaria parasites"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 563472.0,
      "end_time": 565289.0,
      "text": "by running them for a little longer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 565313.0,
      "end_time": 568879.0,
      "text": "and we can identify malaria parasites that are in the blood"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 568903.0,
      "end_time": 572477.0,
      "text": "that we can separate out and detect with something like a centrifuge."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 572501.0,
      "end_time": 576981.0,
      "text": "Another version of this allows me to separate nucleic acids"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 577500.0,
      "end_time": 580562.0,
      "text": "to be able to do nucleic acid tests out in the field itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 581393.0,
      "end_time": 585737.0,
      "text": "Here is another version that allows me to separate bulk samples,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 585761.0,
      "end_time": 587331.0,
      "text": "and then, finally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 587355.0,
      "end_time": 589355.0,
      "text": "something new that we&#39;ve been working on"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 589379.0,
      "end_time": 594174.0,
      "text": "to be able to implement the entire multiplex test on an object like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 594198.0,
      "end_time": 598535.0,
      "text": "So where you do the sample preparation and the chemistry in the same object."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 599360.0,
      "end_time": 600646.0,
      "text": "Now ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 600670.0,
      "end_time": 601939.0,
      "text": "this is all good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 601964.0,
      "end_time": 603871.0,
      "text": "but when you start thinking about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 603895.0,
      "end_time": 605984.0,
      "text": "you have to share these tools with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 606800.0,
      "end_time": 609390.0,
      "text": "And one of the things we did is -- we just got back from Madagascar;"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 609414.0,
      "end_time": 611992.0,
      "text": "this is what clinical trials for malaria look like --"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 612160.0,
      "end_time": 613190.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 613430.0,
      "end_time": 615400.0,
      "text": "You can do this while having coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 615424.0,
      "end_time": 617297.0,
      "text": "But most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 617321.0,
      "end_time": 621383.0,
      "text": "this is a village six hours from any road."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 621856.0,
      "end_time": 626419.0,
      "text": "We are in a room with one of the senior members of the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 626443.0,
      "end_time": 627956.0,
      "text": "and a health care worker."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 627980.0,
      "end_time": 631477.0,
      "text": "It really is this portion of the work that excites me the most --"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 631501.0,
      "end_time": 632659.0,
      "text": "that smile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 632683.0,
      "end_time": 636557.0,
      "text": "to be able to share simple but powerful tools with people around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 637299.0,
      "end_time": 639601.0,
      "text": "Now, I forgot to tell you this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 639625.0,
      "end_time": 642280.0,
      "text": "that all of that cost me 20 cents to make."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 643330.0,
      "end_time": 646212.0,
      "text": "OK, in the negative time I have left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 646236.0,
      "end_time": 648302.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll tell you about the most recent --"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 648326.0,
      "end_time": 649446.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 649470.0,
      "end_time": 651340.0,
      "text": "invention from our lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 651364.0,
      "end_time": 652717.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called Abuzz --"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 653438.0,
      "end_time": 657572.0,
      "text": "the idea that all of you could help us fight mosquitoes;"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 657596.0,
      "end_time": 659863.0,
      "text": "you could all help us track our enemies."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 659887.0,
      "end_time": 663875.0,
      "text": "These are enemies because they cause malaria, Zika, chikungunya, dengue."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 663899.0,
      "end_time": 668683.0,
      "text": "But the challenge is that we actually don&#39;t know where our enemies are."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 668707.0,
      "end_time": 671686.0,
      "text": "The world map for where mosquitoes are is missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 672123.0,
      "end_time": 673866.0,
      "text": "So we started thinking about this."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 673890.0,
      "end_time": 675925.0,
      "text": "There are 3,500 species of mosquitoes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 675949.0,
      "end_time": 677352.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re all very similar."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 677376.0,
      "end_time": 678814.0,
      "text": "Some of them are so identical"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 678839.0,
      "end_time": 682227.0,
      "text": "that even an entomologist cannot identify them under a microscope."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 682916.0,
      "end_time": 684701.0,
      "text": "But they have an Achilles&#39; heel."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 684725.0,
      "end_time": 687925.0,
      "text": "This is what mosquitoes flirting with each other looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 687949.0,
      "end_time": 690178.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a male chasing a female."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 690202.0,
      "end_time": 694230.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re actually talking to each other with their wingbeat frequencies."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 694470.0,
      "end_time": 695870.0,
      "text": "(Buzzing sound)"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 695111.0,
      "end_time": 697468.0,
      "text": "And thus, they have a signature."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 698472.0,
      "end_time": 701836.0,
      "text": "We realized that using a regular phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 701860.0,
      "end_time": 704401.0,
      "text": "a $5-10 flip phone --"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 704425.0,
      "end_time": 706526.0,
      "text": "how many remember what this object is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 706551.0,
      "end_time": 707611.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 707635.0,
      "end_time": 711795.0,
      "text": "We can record these acoustic signatures from mosquitoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 711820.0,
      "end_time": 713756.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll tell you exactly how to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 713780.0,
      "end_time": 715471.0,
      "text": "I caught some mosquitoes outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 715495.0,
      "end_time": 717883.0,
      "text": "Unlike Bill [Gates], I&#39;m not going to release them."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 717907.0,
      "end_time": 718947.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 718971.0,
      "end_time": 721546.0,
      "text": "But I will tell you how to record from this."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 721570.0,
      "end_time": 724120.0,
      "text": "All you do is tap them and they fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 724360.0,
      "end_time": 725377.0,
      "text": "You can first test --"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 725401.0,
      "end_time": 727152.0,
      "text": "I can actually hear that."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 727177.0,
      "end_time": 729631.0,
      "text": "And you bring your phone, which has microphones --"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 729655.0,
      "end_time": 732210.0,
      "text": "it turns out the mics are so damn good already,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 732450.0,
      "end_time": 733285.0,
      "text": "even on regular phones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 733309.0,
      "end_time": 735742.0,
      "text": "that you can pick up this near-field signature."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 735766.0,
      "end_time": 737904.0,
      "text": "And since I&#39;m out of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 737928.0,
      "end_time": 741620.0,
      "text": "let me just play the recording that I made a day ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 741644.0,
      "end_time": 744184.0,
      "text": "(Mosquitoes buzz)"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 744208.0,
      "end_time": 747136.0,
      "text": "This is all the charming sound that you heard before"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 747160.0,
      "end_time": 748343.0,
      "text": "that you all love."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 750606.0,
      "end_time": 752270.0,
      "text": "One of the contexts of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 752510.0,
      "end_time": 755265.0,
      "text": "is that being able to do this with a regular cell phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 755289.0,
      "end_time": 758449.0,
      "text": "allows us to map mosquito species."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 759477.0,
      "end_time": 761169.0,
      "text": "Using a flip phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 761193.0,
      "end_time": 764170.0,
      "text": "we mapped one of the largest acoustic databases"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 764195.0,
      "end_time": 769423.0,
      "text": "with 25 to 20 species of mosquitoes that carry human pathogens."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 769447.0,
      "end_time": 771126.0,
      "text": "And from this and machine learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 771150.0,
      "end_time": 772934.0,
      "text": "anybody who uploads this data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 772958.0,
      "end_time": 774946.0,
      "text": "we can identify and tell the probability"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 774970.0,
      "end_time": 777804.0,
      "text": "of what species of mosquitoes you&#39;re actually working with."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 777828.0,
      "end_time": 780643.0,
      "text": "We call this Abuzz, and if any of you want to sign up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 780667.0,
      "end_time": 781885.0,
      "text": "just go to the website."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 782343.0,
      "end_time": 783985.0,
      "text": "Let me close with something"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 784900.0,
      "end_time": 786310.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s very important and dear to my heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 787324.0,
      "end_time": 791271.0,
      "text": "One of the challenges of today is we have terrible problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 791295.0,
      "end_time": 794193.0,
      "text": "We have a billion people with absolutely no health care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 794217.0,
      "end_time": 796342.0,
      "text": "climate change, biodiversity loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 796366.0,
      "end_time": 797550.0,
      "text": "on and on and on."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 798460.0,
      "end_time": 800996.0,
      "text": "And we hope that science is going to provide the answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 801410.0,
      "end_time": 803558.0,
      "text": "But before you leave this theatre today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 803582.0,
      "end_time": 805336.0,
      "text": "I want you to promise one thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 805745.0,
      "end_time": 808123.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to make science accessible --"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 808886.0,
      "end_time": 811250.0,
      "text": "not just to the people who can afford it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 811490.0,
      "end_time": 812930.0,
      "text": "but a billion others who can&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 813581.0,
      "end_time": 817597.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s make science and scientific literacy a human right."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 819384.0,
      "end_time": 824590.0,
      "text": "The moment that you pass the tingling feeling of making a discovery"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 824830.0,
      "end_time": 825593.0,
      "text": "to another child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 826263.0,
      "end_time": 830550.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re enabling them to be the next group of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 830790.0,
      "end_time": 832186.0,
      "text": "who will actually solve these problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 832211.0,
      "end_time": 833386.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 833410.0,
      "end_time": 836788.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}